Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.86,0:03:22.46,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}迷わずにdive in dive in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:24.82,OPED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Stand up 壊してく the nonsense
